          "Don’t Look Up"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ", with Adam, who wrote the screenplay and directed the movie. I’m thrilled to see it being hailed as one the most important climate films ever. As the movie launches today, I feel tremendous gratitude to all of our "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
