          "Daily Poster"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " subscribers for supporting the journalism that is the foundation for this kind of project, which will send a powerful message to millions of people across the planet. As you will see when you watch it, this movie spotlights many themes, controversies, and power struggles that we report on every day here at "
