      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "This movie started out as so many things do: as a conversation between two longtime friends who were bemoaning the state of the world. Adam and I were lamenting how the political class and corporate media were ignoring the climate crisis threatening all life on the planet. At one point, I said the whole thing felt like an asteroid is heading toward Earth and nobody seems to care — and that became the seed of this film. You can "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            4
          ],
          1,
          "click here"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " to watch Adam recount this origin story with the cast."
